cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.NE, cs.CE 

This paper discusses the challenges and solutions related to cloud autoscaling, which is a topic that falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the need to improve the long-term stability and sustainability of cloud ecosystem, which is related to Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper proposes to transpose ecological principles, theories, and models into cloud autoscaling analogues, which is related to Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE).
